Version 0.2.4
=============
    + Fixed a bug causing irrecoverable "ring buffer overflow" error
    for some channels

    + Minor improvements in logging and error handling

Version 0.2.3
=============
    + Set SO_REUSEADDR flag for sockets receiving multicast to
    improve co-existing with other applications receiving multicast

    + Improve some error messages

    + Added few more parameters to the configuration file

Version 0.2.2
=============
    + HTTP protocol now supports the URL scheme used by udpxy
    for improved compatibility with some third-parity software

    + Set socket priority for HTTP-streaming sockets

Version 0.2.1
=============
    + Properly detect HTTP client disconnects - prevent
    resource leakage under certain conditions

    + Fixed bug which made first few seconds of HTTP stream
    unplayable

Version 0.2
===========
    * Added HTTP "continuous download" streaming

    + Added support for RTP UDP multicast sources

    + Improved support of multiple clients with same
    IP address via RTSP

    + Set IP TOS and socket priority for RTP streams


Version 0.1
===========
    Initial release.
